about.description:
Google Cloud IoT API client library is a Google Cloud service that lets client applications communicate with the Google Cloud IoT platform. Google Cloud IoT is a complete set of tools to connect, process, store, and analyze data both at the edge and in the cloud. The platform consists of scalable, fully-managed cloud services as well as an integrated software stack for edge/on-premises computing with machine learning capabilities for all your IoT needs.
See the [quick start guide](https://googleapis.dev/python/iot/latest/index.html#quick-start).
about.summary: Google Cloud IoT API client library

name: google-cloud-iot
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "google-cloud-iot" %}
{% set version = "2.0.0" %}
{% set sha256 = "e06342b691f1dd7ec5ebb15df1747918bdd717ad6414d711d45b42122c099b70" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.6
    - pip >=18.1
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - google-api-core-grpc >=1.22.0,<2.0.0dev
    - grpc-google-iam-v1 >=0.12.3,<0.13.0dev
    - proto-plus >=1.4.0
    - libcst >=0.2.5

test:
  imports:
    - grpc
    - google.cloud.iot
    - google.cloud.iot_v1

about:
  home: https://github.com/googleapis/python-iot
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_family: Apache
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Google Cloud IoT API client library
  description: "Google Cloud IoT API client library is a Google Cloud service that lets client applications communicate with the Google Cloud IoT platform. Google Cloud IoT is a complete set of tools to connect, process, store, and analyze data both at the edge and in the cloud. The platform consists of scalable, fully-managed\
    \ cloud services as well as an integrated software stack for edge/on-premises computing with machine learning capabilities for all your IoT needs.\nSee the [quick start guide](https://googleapis.dev/python/iot/latest/index.html#quick-start)."

  doc_url: https://googleapis.dev/python/iot/latest/index.html
  dev_url: https://github.com/googleapis/python-iot

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - parthea
